Package com.iontrading.mkv

The classes in this package pose the core of the ION Bus Java API.
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BootstrapConfigurationListener  
    GlobalEventListener
    Interface for getting notifications for global events like publication, supplies, chain modification, queue supplies, function call/response, transaction call/response.
    GlobalEventListenerFactory
    Factory Interface for creating GlobalEventListener object
    example: How to create a custom GlobalEventListenerFactory and use it to receive global events
    IMkvEntitlementResultInfo  
    IMkvTickData
    Public interface for reporting performance measurement ticks
    MkvAuthenticationProcessLogoutResponseListener
    Listener class to get the results of enterprise authentication logout request validation (for SAML / OpenID).
    MkvAuthenticationRequestCreationListener
    Listener class to get the results of enterprise authentication request creation (for SAML / OpenID).
    MkvAuthenticationSingleLogoutRequestCreationListener
    Listener class to get the results of enterprise authentication single logout request creation (for SAML / OpenID).
    MkvCallerInfo  
    MkvLifeCycleListener
    Persistent subscriptions allows to subscribe to records regardless of the data being available at the time the subscription is carried on; data will eventually arrive once made available; declarative subscriptions implement transparent resumption of data flow after temporary unavailability of data.
    MkvLog
    This is the interface of all log services exported or used by this API.
    MkvLogExt
    This is the interface of all log services exported or used by this API.
    MkvLogSplitListener
    This is the interface for listener to new log split file creation.
    MkvOnBehalfOfFeatureLicenseManager
    This interface provides the access to on-behalf-of requests of by-feature licenses.
    MkvServicePasswordListener
    Interface needed to retrieve configuration passwords from the Daemon.
    MkvSubscriptionRequest
    This object wraps all the required information related to a record subscription request matching a MkvRecordset publication.
    MkvSubscriptionRequestListener
    When creating a Recordset on publisher side, an optional MkvSubscriptionRequestListener object can be provided to programmatically react to record subscription requests matching the Recordset.
    MkvSupply
    This interface wraps a ION Bus supply into a Java object.
    ReadinessProvider
    The application provider for the readiness status.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Mkv
    Mkv is the entry-point class to all services offered by this API.
    MkvAuthenticationProcessLogoutResponse
    This class represents the outcome of the ProcessLogoutRequest (for SAML / OpenID).
    MkvAuthenticationRequestInfo
    This class wraps the property of an authentication request (for SAML / OpenID).
    MkvAuthenticationSingleLogoutRequestInfo
    This class wraps the property of an authentication single logout request (for SAML / OpenID).
    MkvByFeatureReportQoS  
    MkvChain
    The MkvChain class wraps an ION Bus Chain in a Java Object.
    MkvComponent
    The MkvComponent class wraps a ION Bus component in a Java Object.
    MkvCustomStatsManager
    This class provides a manager for Custom Statistics tables.
    MkvCustomStatsTable
    This class provides a container for custom statistics of a given category.
    MkvE2EDelaySampler
    The MkvE2EDelaySampler provides feeding functionality for custom End To End Delay statistics.
    MkvE2ETickData
    This class cares about collecting tick by tick measures and computing their distribution into time buckets.
    MkvEntitlementManager
    This class provides access to entitlement service facilities.
    MkvEntitlementReason  
    MkvEntitlementRequest
    This class represent a request for the entitlement server.
    MkvEntitlementResultInfo
    Class describing extended information about entitlement result, including the reason for the result and the list of matched rule ids, if any.
    MkvEntitlements
    The feature allows users to query Entitlement Server with complex criteria for downloading entire lists of entitlements at once.
    MkvEntitlements.CommonData
    The common data class
    This class abstracts the common features of a query/response
    MkvEntitlements.Element
    Generic element of a query/response
    This class represents the anchestor of any Service/Container/Object created for entitlements query or response
    MkvEntitlements.EntitlementsIterator
    The entiterator class This class allows both client-side and server-side to iterate over a query/response It can be created using a Query object (for server-side usage) or using a Response object (for client-side usage) The class implements the Iterator interface
    MkvEntitlements.Query
    The query class
    This class contains all the information required to perform a query to the Entitlement Server
    MkvEntitlements.Response
    The response class This class contains all the information that are returned by the Entitlement Server as result of a query Each element is an object for which the user possesses the entitlement
    MkvESDataAdapterProvider  
    MkvFunction
    The MkvFunction class wraps a ION Bus Function in a Java Object.
    MkvGroup
    The MkvGroup class wraps a ION Platform Group in a Java Object.
    MkvLicenseManager

    MkvLogManager
    This class provides access to the log facilities exported by this API.
    MkvObject
